name: Monster in the Forest of Death

metadata.name: Fire Head "Deep Ravines"
metadata.description:
" Fire Head "
Nobody knows the exact origin. But it is assumed to be a mutant creature walking on two legs. The highlight is that it has a fire head. It had a body similar to that of a human. But it is more powerful, with a body that is larger than a human and has sharp claws. Has a habit of being quite irritable all the time
Its movement will cause a slight vibration in the immediate vicinity.
Usually live in deep ravines or areas with separate land.
The fire that exists on the head will burn all the time. and it will burn even more When it's time to fight.

" Monster In The Forest of Death "
